Biography
American economist and CEO of Gerber Products, an infant foods wholesaler, products manufacturer and clothing maker.  With interests in merchandise marketing, Piergallini has a BA in Economics and an MBA in Finance. He presents a familial image in photographs showing him in his shirtsleeves with a baby in his arms.

