Insider Activity


Individual




Alfred A. Piergallini



Mr. Alfred A. Piergallini is Independent Director at Central Garden & Pet Co., Independent Director at Comerica, Inc., and Chairman at Desert Trail Consulting LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Central Garden & Pet Co., Comerica, Inc., and Comerica Bank (Dallas, Texas).
Mr. Piergallini was previously employed as Chairman by Wisconsin Cheese Group, Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Novartis Consumer Health Worldwide, President & Chief Executive Officer by Novartis Consumer Health North America, and Vice Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Gerber Products Co.



